  <caaml:metaData>
    <caaml:comment>Observers: Carbonari/Cloutier/Hannan.  Pit dug to 230 cm.  Rain line near 5400 feet at 1100 but raised to over 6800 feet by 1400.  Wet.  Cracking and very small loose wet slides triggered by skiing on steep slopes.  Top few cm of snow saturated at 6000 feet.  Pinwheels and rollerballs in abundance.  Warming temps through the day.  Wet....</caaml:comment>
